[{"Code":"en","Title":"[Regional] Conversions","Slug":"conversions","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"a0a277f0-421f-467a-b9d3-1f2d58b8f5d9\">You can perform currency conversions between your available currency balances. </p><p data-block-id=\"82ad36aa-7746-48c8-8af0-6a8ff0fd1f33\">On your Xendit Dashboard, from any of your balances, initiate the “Convert” process and select your destination currency, which must be one of your open currency balances. </p><p data-block-id=\"132aecfb-d30d-4616-ae54-90d82fc910a0\">You’ll be quoted a rate for that currency pair, as well as the amount you’ll receive. The rate refreshes after 1 minute.</p><p data-block-id=\"c2ac6561-ba30-4c0d-8e5c-1f931f9e3c39\">If you accept, complete the flow and you’ll immediately receive the converted amount in your destination currency balance. </p><p data-block-id=\"1ebd2e88-e21f-4057-9bc4-598ea654d347\">Xendit charges no fees for conversion and uses market competitive FX rates.</p><p data-block-id=\"a88de6a8-d873-4668-9e48-da1b3a6a25b7\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);background:transparent;font-family:Arial;font-size:11pt;font-weight:400;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\" type=\"spanMark\"><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:747px;height:593px;\" type=\"spanNode\"><img data-block-id=\"d0bf817d-36f0-43e9-990c-ffd6ae48bb52\" src=\"https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXernQ0mO8sTrDw4yZ6ebqBqkavToVzCziMHDJrX7Gxz-9laLlpexCvxZH9aCehuK5RLl6SqW2IN-cipzEgD_INgaPJ8Qx2d14Rltd03RnsVIavJs8WGC3zuyDNQzuJII4jYfWDo3w?key=8rOVuiacFnkRIbTxpzwbVBcX\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"747\" height=\"593\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px;\"></span></span></p><h4 data-block-id=\"b0c3b900-b56f-403a-a082-fece3ac9b2b8\">Available currency pairs for conversions</h4><p data-block-id=\"5c654883-ede6-4828-a02e-aacf630ebeb3\">[TBD]</p><p data-block-id=\"ca9f76d5-b538-4dce-8b10-3e5a69083155\"></p>","SeoTitle":"[Regional] Conversions","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Conversions","Slug":"conversions","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"Conversions","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"Conversions","Slug":"conversions","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"Conversions","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"[Regional] Conversions","Slug":"conversions","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"a0a277f0-421f-467a-b9d3-1f2d58b8f5d9\">You can perform currency conversions between your available currency balances. </p><p data-block-id=\"82ad36aa-7746-48c8-8af0-6a8ff0fd1f33\">On your Xendit Dashboard, from any of your balances, initiate the “Convert” process and select your destination currency, which must be one of your open currency balances. </p><p data-block-id=\"132aecfb-d30d-4616-ae54-90d82fc910a0\">You’ll be quoted a rate for that currency pair, as well as the amount you’ll receive. The rate refreshes after 1 minute.</p><p data-block-id=\"c2ac6561-ba30-4c0d-8e5c-1f931f9e3c39\">If you accept, complete the flow and you’ll immediately receive the converted amount in your destination currency balance. </p><p data-block-id=\"1ebd2e88-e21f-4057-9bc4-598ea654d347\">Xendit charges no fees for conversion and uses market competitive FX rates.</p><p data-block-id=\"a88de6a8-d873-4668-9e48-da1b3a6a25b7\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);background:transparent;font-family:Arial;font-size:11pt;font-weight:400;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\" type=\"spanMark\"><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:747px;height:593px;\" type=\"spanNode\"><img data-block-id=\"d0bf817d-36f0-43e9-990c-ffd6ae48bb52\" src=\"https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXernQ0mO8sTrDw4yZ6ebqBqkavToVzCziMHDJrX7Gxz-9laLlpexCvxZH9aCehuK5RLl6SqW2IN-cipzEgD_INgaPJ8Qx2d14Rltd03RnsVIavJs8WGC3zuyDNQzuJII4jYfWDo3w?key=8rOVuiacFnkRIbTxpzwbVBcX\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"747\" height=\"593\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px;\"></span></span></p><h4 data-block-id=\"b0c3b900-b56f-403a-a082-fece3ac9b2b8\">Available currency pairs for conversions</h4><p data-block-id=\"5c654883-ede6-4828-a02e-aacf630ebeb3\">[TBD]</p><p data-block-id=\"ca9f76d5-b538-4dce-8b10-3e5a69083155\"></p>","SeoTitle":"[Regional] Conversions","Description":null}]